## 9. Right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority

You may lodge a complaint with the supervisory authority of your habitual
residence, place of work, or place of the alleged infringement (Art. 77).
Examples: ICO (UK), CNIL (France), Datatilsynet (Denmark), BfDI (Germany),
AEPD (Spain). [LEGAL REVIEW REQUIRED] — name the lead supervisory authority
for the controller.

## 10. Article 30 record

